node.text: Thank you to everyone for all the Dam Good Times we have had over these past 8 years. Normally we’d invite all of you to our anniversary party, and boogie the night away, but due to the current circumstances we had to switch it up this year. To everyone that purchased our beer boxes before they sold out, CHEERS! We hope you are enjoying the selection of beers we sent out to you. If you didn't get a chance to grab a box, stop by any of our locations to pick up some beer to-go or dine in and have a meal and pint with us. Cheers to many more years of excellent beer! #damgoodtimes #8damyears #sdbeer

Island Sunshine - Kettle Sour with Peach and Guava, 5.5% ABV

The peach and guava in this beer gives it lots of tropical notes and balances out the tart flavors from the souring process. Enjoy this beer by the pool, with friends at a BBQ or at any Summer activity in the sun.

node.text:
Here at the Beav, we believe if you’re going to do something do it good -- Dam Good. That’s why we created the Dam Good IPA Pack, a mix of our best IPAs, to satisfy hop heads everywhere. We included our new West Coast IPA No Worries, our hazy IPA Hazers Gonna Haze, the inimitable Phantom Bride IPA, and even brought back one of Tom’s favorites, Mosaic Double IPA. If you can’t decide what to drink for National IPA Day on August 5th, don’t worry, we’ve got you covered with the Dam Good IPA Pack.
Each 8-Pack Includes:
(2) No Worries IPA – 6.2% ABV, 45 IBUs
(2) Hazers Gonna Haze – 6.6% ABV, 35 IBUs
(2) Mosaic IPA – 8.8% ABV, 60 IBUs
(2) Phantom Bride IPA – 7.1% ABV, 60 IBUs
Mixed packs will be available year-round, rolling out to retailers & available at: @belchingbeaverpub980 @belchingbeaveroside @belchingbeavernorthpark
